imdb.plot outline: In the Northeast of Brazil, land of the social bandit, the Royal Family from the fictional kingdom of Serafia loses its heir due to a betrayal and a planned accident. Once thought she had been dead for years, King August finds out that his daughter Aurora(Aucena) is alive and now he is determined to find her. Go back to your childhood days with this well-written enchanting and humorous fairy-tale inspired by Brazil's northeast culture.
imdb.title: The Enchanted Tale
plot: In the Northeast of Brazil, land of the social bandit, the Royal Family from the fictional kingdom of Serafia loses its heir due to a betrayal and a planned accident. Once thought she had been dead for years, King August finds out that his daughter Aurora(Aucena) is alive and now he is determined to find her. Go back to your childhood days with this well-written enchanting and humorous fairy-tale inspired by Brazil's northeast culture.::Natalia D.
